  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/4267d0c1a4b9dc4cb30efd10b9fc02ba.avif?t=1768314743\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STORY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as the High Priestess MARY, whose mission is to defend the statue of the Mother Goddess ALEA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the statue is destroyed by the elves, the kingdom of Saint Aquinas will fall before the cursed army of the great sorceress HERA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/5bbe37c4278ca64e982fcf084648fbc4.poster.avif?t=1768314743\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/5bbe37c4278ca64e982fcf084648fbc4.webm?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/5bbe37c4278ca64e982fcf084648fbc4.mp4?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DIVINE POWER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can request the support of the goddess Alea with the Prayer skill to accumulate divine power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This divine power will allow you to perform miracles:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can summon divine soldiers from the blessed army; among them are divine knights and nuns of blessing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can heal all the soldiers of your sacred guard individually or in groups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can create a divine image of yourself to block the attackers' movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can communicate with all your soldiers at the same time to summon them to your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/2bec5d32e841c073a12952cc083a86fc.poster.avif?t=1768314743\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/2bec5d32e841c073a12952cc083a86fc.webm?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/2bec5d32e841c073a12952cc083a86fc.mp4?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GAMEPLAY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a while, a group of enemies will appear and rush towards the statue to destroy it. You can't attack enemies yourself; for that, you need the Holy Soldiers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you'll gain experience and increase your power level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This will help you improve your skills and those of your Blessed Guard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/c06be59dd4172ead6392b4735b53e12a.avif?t=1768314743\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras_big/c06be59dd4172ead6392b4735b53e12a.avif?t=1768314743 width=800 height=1067 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BONUS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will include a roguelike/STORE system allowing you to unlock new units to fight more effectively thanks to the divine rewards you collect in battle.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/4267d0c1a4b9dc4cb30efd10b9fc02ba.avif?t=1768314743\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STORY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as the High Priestess MARY, whose mission is to defend the statue of the Mother Goddess ALEA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the statue is destroyed by the elves, the kingdom of Saint Aquinas will fall before the cursed army of the great sorceress HERA.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/5bbe37c4278ca64e982fcf084648fbc4.poster.avif?t=1768314743\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/5bbe37c4278ca64e982fcf084648fbc4.webm?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/5bbe37c4278ca64e982fcf084648fbc4.mp4?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DIVINE POWER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can request the support of the goddess Alea with the Prayer skill to accumulate divine power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This divine power will allow you to perform miracles:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can summon divine soldiers from the blessed army; among them are divine knights and nuns of blessing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can heal all the soldiers of your sacred guard individually or in groups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can create a divine image of yourself to block the attackers' movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can communicate with all your soldiers at the same time to summon them to your side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/2bec5d32e841c073a12952cc083a86fc.poster.avif?t=1768314743\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/2bec5d32e841c073a12952cc083a86fc.webm?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/2bec5d32e841c073a12952cc083a86fc.mp4?t=1768314743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GAMEPLAY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a while, a group of enemies will appear and rush towards the statue to destroy it. You can't attack enemies yourself; for that, you need the Holy Soldiers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you'll gain experience and increase your power level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This will help you improve your skills and those of your Blessed Guard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras/c06be59dd4172ead6392b4735b53e12a.avif?t=1768314743\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3677580/extras_big/c06be59dd4172ead6392b4735b53e12a.avif?t=1768314743 width=800 height=1067 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BONUS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will include a roguelike/STORE system allowing you to unlock new units to fight more effectively thanks to the divine rewards you collect in battle.</p>",
